https://arvid.app/dinofend-privacy-policy:
Dinofend Privacy Policy
No Tracking or Data Collection
We do not track or collect any personal information from you while using our app. We do not gather any data regarding your interactions within the app or track your activities outside of the app. Your privacy is important to us, and we do not engage in any tracking or third-party data sharing.
Hand Tracking
Hand tracking is used within the app to enhance your interaction with the game. The hand tracking data is processed
entirely on your device
and is
not saved or transmitted
to any external servers. We do not store any information about your hand movements after they are used in the app.
Voice Recording
Voice commands are used for gameplay interaction. The voice data is recorded and processed
locally on your device
in real time.
No voice recordings are saved
or transmitted to any servers. Your voice input is used solely for the purpose of gameplay and is discarded once it has been processed.
No External Sharing
We do not share or transmit any data to third parties, whether collected within the app or through hand tracking and voice recording functionalities. All processing happens directly on your device, ensuring that your data remains private.
Terms & Conditions
These
Terms and Conditions
("Terms") govern your use of the Dinofend ("App") developed for
Apple Vision Pro
. By using the App, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms.
Acceptance of Terms
By downloading, installing, or using the App, you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use the App.
License to Use the App
We grant you a personal, non-transferable, and non-exclusive license to use the App on your Apple Vision Pro device. This license is subject to the conditions outlined in these Terms.
Data Privacy and Collection
We respect your privacy and do not collect, track, or share any personal data unless explicitly stated in this Privacy Policy.The App may use
hand tracking
and
voice recording
for interaction and gameplay, but all data is processed
locally on your device
and
not saved
or transmitted.We do not track your activities outside of the app, and no data is stored or shared with third parties.
Hand Tracking and Voice Commands
The app uses
hand tracking
and
voice commands
for gameplay. The
hand tracking data
and
voice input
are processed in real-time
on the device
and are
not stored
or transmitted.
You acknowledge that using the hand tracking and voice features may require you to grant permission to access the camera and microphone on your device.
App Usage and Health Disclaimer
The app is designed for entertainment and interaction in
immersive environments
on the Apple Vision Pro.
The app does not require you to physically move
. It uses hand tracking and voice commands for interaction, and all actions are carried out within the virtual environment.
Prolonged use of the Apple Vision Pro or engaging in immersive experiences may cause discomfort, including
eye strain
,
dizziness
, or
motion sickness
. We recommend taking breaks and following recommended usage guidelines for immersive experiences.
Liability Disclaimer
: The app is not responsible for any
injuries, accidents, or damage
that may occur while in
full immersion
. We recommend using the app in a safe, clear environment and remaining seated or in a stationary position while playing. Users should also ensure they have enough space to avoid any risk of injury.
